Package: glmmTMBaug
Title: Penalized Estimation via Data Augmentation for GLMMs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Tina", "KoÅ¡uta", , "tina.kosuta@mf.uni-lj.si", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for penalized estimation in generalized linear mixed models
    using a data augmentation approach. Built on top of glmmTMB, it allows automatic
    tuning of penalty strength for binomial, Poisson, and Gaussian families with a
    single level of random effects.
